'''Aṭṭan''' d tagnit targamant yettaɣen [[tafekka]] n [[afgan|wemdan]] neɣ [[agerru|agerru-ynes]] ayen i d-igellun s usenzem d uɣilif neɣ tamumt deg twuriwin d [[Atmelli|utmelli]] i wemdan [[igem|yugmen]] (i yuɣ waṭṭan). Irem n waṭṭan d win yettusmersen (yettusxedmen) i wsenmel n yal ugur [[tafekka|afekkan]] neɣ [[Tikdewt]] neɣ [[tamsedfart]] neɣ [[asken|isekna]] isetmellayen (yessɛyawen) neɣ ibeddilen irnawen deg tmuska n twuriwin. [[Tasnaṭṭant]] tga d [[tamusni]] yeɣɣaṛen aṭṭanen-a. Ma d tamusni yeɣɣaṛen asesmel anarray n waṭṭanen yemgaraden iga d [[Tusemelṭant]]. Ma d tamusni yezdin yakk aṭṭanen n wemdan d tirrayin n [[Tawessna|usennefru-nsent]] isem-is [[tasnujjya]] <br/> 
Dɣa aṭas n waṭṭanen zemren ad aɣen ula d [[iɣersiwen]] ama d [[agrad|imegruden]] (wid yettidiren ɣer wemdan) neɣ d izagiren (wid yettidiren deg lexla). Tazrawt n waṭṭanen ayti imekknen iɣersiwen isem-is [[Abidar|abidaṛ]].

